<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome - Personal Website</title>
    <!-- Your Custom Favicon -->
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="<%= basePath %>/images/favicon.png">
    <link rel="apple-touch-icon" href="<%= basePath %>/images/favicon.png">
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #495057;
            background-image: url('<%= basePath %>/images/nature-bg.jpg');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            background-attachment: fixed;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        header {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            padding: 1rem 0;
            position: fixed;
            width: 100%;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
        }

        nav {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .logo {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #4CAF50; /* Nature green logo text */
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .nav-links {
            display: flex;
            list-style: none;
            gap: 2rem;
        }

        .nav-links a {
            color: #333;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .nav-links a:hover {
            color: #4CAF50;
        }

        .hero {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            text-align: center;
            color: #333;
            padding-top: 80px;
            background: none; /* Let body background show through */
        }

        .hero-content {
            max-width: 800px;
            animation: fadeInUp 1s ease-out;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7); /* Add a background for readability */
            padding: 2rem;
            border-radius: 15px;
            backdrop-filter: blur(5px);
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 3.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            color: #212529;
        }

        .hero p {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            color: #495057;
        }

        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #4CAF50;
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(76, 175, 80, 0.3);
        }

        .cta-button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(76, 175, 80, 0.4);
            background: #45a049;
        }

        .features {
            padding: 80px 0;
            background-color: rgba(248, 249, 250, 0.9); /* Semi-transparent off-white */
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        }

        .features-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 2rem;
            margin-top: 3rem;
        }

        .feature-card {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95); /* Slightly more opaque cards */
            padding: 2rem;
            border-radius: 15px;
            text-align: center;
            border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .feature-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }

        .feature-icon {
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            color: #4CAF50;
        }

        .feature-card h3 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .section-title {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .section-subtitle {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: #6c757d;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        footer {
            background: rgba(52, 58, 64, 0.9); /* Semi-transparent dark */
            color: #f8f9fa; /* Keep text light */
            text-align: center;
            padding: 2rem 0;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        }

        @keyframes fadeInUp {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(30px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .hero h1 {
                font-size: 2.5rem;
            }
            
            .nav-links {
                gap: 1rem;
            }
            
            .features-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <nav class="container">
            <a href="<%= basePath %>/" class="logo">
                <i class="fas fa-user-circle"></i> Personal Hub
            </a>
            <ul class="nav-links">
                <li><a href="<%= basePath %>/">Home</a></li>
                <li><a href="https://profile.mythiru.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Profile</a></li>
                <li><a href="<%= basePath %>/login">Login</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <main>
        <section class="hero">
            <div class="hero-content">
                <h1>Welcome to My Personal Hub</h1>
                <p>A secure, private space to manage your tasks, notes, and files with style and efficiency.</p>
                <a href="<%= basePath %>/login" class="cta-button">
                    <i class="fas fa-sign-in-alt"></i> Access Dashboard
                </a>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="features">
            <div class="container">
                <h2 class="section-title">Powerful Features</h2>
                <p class="section-subtitle">Everything you need to stay organized and productive in one beautiful interface.</p>
                
                <div class="features-grid">
                    <div class="feature-card">
                        <div class="feature-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-tasks"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3>Smart Checklists</h3>
                        <p>Create and manage your tasks with an intuitive checklist system. Stay organized and track your progress effortlessly.</p>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="feature-card">
                        <div class="feature-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-sticky-note"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3>Rich Notes</h3>
                        <p>Capture your thoughts, ideas, and important information with a powerful note-taking system that keeps everything at your fingertips.</p>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="feature-card">
                        <div class="feature-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-cloud-upload-alt"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3>File Management</h3>
                        <p>Upload, organize, and access your files and photos securely. Support for multiple file types with easy download and management.</p>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="feature-card">
                        <div class="feature-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3>Secure Access</h3>
                        <p>Your personal data is protected with robust authentication and security measures. Only you can access your private dashboard.</p>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="feature-card">
                        <div class="feature-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-mobile-alt"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3>Responsive Design</h3>
                        <p>Access your personal hub from any device. The interface adapts beautifully to desktop, tablet, and mobile screens.</p>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="feature-card">
                        <div class="feature-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-palette"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3>Beautiful Interface</h3>
                        <p>Enjoy a modern, clean, and visually appealing interface that makes managing your personal data a pleasure.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <div class="container">
            <p>&copy; 2024 Personal Hub. Built with care and attention to detail.</p>
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
